in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.complex

Class ComplexFractalGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.FractalGenerator
      • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.PixelFractalGenerator
        • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.complex.ComplexFractalGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pannable, Zoomable, java.io.Serializable

    public final class ComplexFractalGenerator
extends PixelFractalGenerator
    The actual fractal plotter for Julia, Newton, Nova (both Mandelbrot and Julia variants),Secant and Mandelbrot Sets using an iterative algorithm. The Buddhabrot technique (naive algorithm) is also implemented (of sorts) for all modes. Various (21) Coloring modes
